  rdfs:label "Administrative Location"@en;
  <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Represents an administrative or geopolitical geographic area used to organize, classify, or associate meteorological information. Examples include countries, states, provinces, districts, municipalities, or other officially defined regions used for reporting and analysis."@en .

